name: Over (mighty_bear246)
description:
A dark, dangerous world.

But after some time, is it the same?

The end of something, leads to the beginning of another.

Made in a week for Brackeys Game Jam 2023.1!

This was my first game jam, and it was so hectic, but still so fun!

sounds taken from itch.io, soundjay and mixkit

--note

if you get stuck, and the game hasn't said over, then jump into the void to reset your position :)

also there probably are some bugs that I may have accidentally looked over lol :D
